			</TEXT>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_ARENA_STRATEGY">
			<TEXT>
				The Arena is a judicial building that raises the [ICON_GOLD] Gold and [ICON_HAPPINESS_1] Happiness of a city.
			</TEXT>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_BUILDING_ARENA_DESC">
			<Text>While it hardly lends itself to fairness, arguably the oldest method to settle disputes is the duel. Taken to an extreme, this too can be the basis of a judicial system. What it lacks in meaningful justice it makes up for in low operating costs, not to mention the spoils of any fallen combantants.</Text>
		</Row>
